<p>I suppose I shouldn&#8217;t be surprised by the piling-on, but just need to ask &#8211; has anyone every tried to access Ticketmaster when Springsteen tickets go on sale, or a similar event? Here&#8217;s a website that&#8217;s been in business from day 1 of the internet, and it becomes totally unusable under circumstances that are a cakewalk compared to the healthcare exchange.</p>
