<a href="http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/culture/2013/11/new-yorker-magazine-cover-obamacare-website-troubles.html"> newyorker.com/online/blogs/c…</a> <a href="http://t.co/yJWfRuO8GK" rel="nofollow">http://t.co/yJWfRuO8GK</a>&mdash; <br />billmon (@billmon1) <a href='http://twitter.com/#!/billmon1/status/396712844064219136' data-datetime='2013-11-02T18:58:07+00:00'>November 02, 2013</a></p></blockquote>
