				My post at @<a href='http://twitter.com/HarvardCorpGov'>HarvardCorpGov</a>, on Incentives and Ideology (my HLR online thing): <a href="http://wp.me/p4Hniv-gGh"> wp.me/p4Hniv-gGh</a> 				<a href="http://twitter.com/JamesYKwak/statuses/481287074918567937" class="timesince">3&nbsp;months&nbsp;ago</a>
			</li>

			
			<li>
				Wait - now Eric Cantor is a moderate? <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/11/us/politics/cantors-loss-a-bad-omen-for-moderates.html"> nytimes.com/2014/06/11/us/…</a> 				<a href="http://twitter.com/JamesYKwak/statuses/476745568102797312" class="timesince">3&nbsp;months&nbsp;ago</a>
